const publishDate = new Date("March 16 2026");
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "5 min read";

const isPublished = new Date().getTime() >= publishDate.getTime();

---

<BaseLayout
  title="Top 5 Hidden Spring Cleaning Spots Athens AL"
  description={isPublished ? "Full Article: Top 5 Hidden Areas to Focus on During Spring Cleaning in Athens, AL" : "Coming Soon: Top 5 Hidden Areas to Focus on During Spring Cleaning in Athens, AL"}
  ogImage="https://storage.googleapis.com/msgsndr/iKQIBhpKVL2XVPgU7HMd/media/6920802945dc047d65b4ec5d.png"
>
  <SchemaMarkup
    type="article"
    title="Top 5 Hidden Areas to Focus on During Spring Cleaning in Athens, AL"
    description="Athens homeowners: Do not miss these spots! Discover the top 5 hidden areas to focus on during your annual spring deep cleaning."
    publishDate="March 16 2026"
    author={author}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#FFA985]/20 text-[#FFA985] rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
          Deep Cleaning
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          Top 5 Hidden Areas to Focus on During Spring Cleaning in Athens, AL
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          {isPublished ? "Expert Cleaning Guide" : "Coming March 16 2026."}
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>March 16 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>What Are the Top 5 Hidden Areas to Focus on During Spring Cleaning in Athens, AL?</h2>
<p><strong>Spring cleaning is the perfect time to tackle those often-overlooked areas in your home. In Athens, AL, focusing on these hidden spots can transform your living space and enhance your home's longevity. Our expert cleaning specialists at The Valley Clean Team have identified the top five hidden areas you shouldn't miss.</strong></p>

<h3>1. Baseboards and Moldings: The Foundation of Cleanliness</h3>
<p>Baseboards and moldings are often neglected, yet they gather dust and grime over time. In the humidity of Athens, AL, this can lead to discoloration and damage.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Why Focus Here?</strong> A clean baseboard enhances the overall look and feel of your rooms, giving them a polished, well-maintained appearance.</li>
  <li><strong>How to Clean:</strong> Use a damp microfiber cloth to wipe away dust. For stubborn stains, a gentle cleaning solution works wonders.</li>
</ul>

<h3>2. Ceiling Fans: Circulate Fresh, Clean Air</h3>
<p>Ceiling fans circulate air but also accumulate dust and allergens, especially during the winter months when they're not in use.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Why Focus Here?</strong> Clean fans improve air quality and ensure efficient operation.</li>
  <li><strong>How to Clean:</strong> Place an old pillowcase over each blade and pull it back, trapping dust inside. Follow up with a damp cloth for any remaining residue.</li>
</ul>

<h3>3. Behind Appliances: The Hidden Dust Havens</h3>
<p>Areas behind your stove, refrigerator, and other appliances are breeding grounds for dust and grime. In Athens, these areas can also attract pests if left unchecked.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Why Focus Here?</strong> Cleaning behind appliances prevents pest infestations and keeps your kitchen smelling fresh.</li>
  <li><strong>How to Clean:</strong> Carefully move appliances to access these spaces, vacuum up dust, and wipe down surfaces with a suitable cleaner.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4. Window Tracks: Let in the Light Without the Dirt</h3>
<p>Window tracks can become clogged with dust, dead insects, and debris, hindering smooth operation and detracting from your view.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Why Focus Here?</strong> Clean tracks ensure your windows open easily and let in maximum light.</li>
  <li><strong>How to Clean:</strong> Use a toothbrush to loosen debris, then vacuum it up. Finish with a damp cloth to remove any remaining dirt.</li>
</ul>

<h3>5. Under Furniture: The Overlooked Dust Bunnies</h3>
<p>Areas beneath beds, sofas, and other large furniture items collect dust and allergens over time.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Why Focus Here?</strong> A dust-free home reduces allergy symptoms and creates a healthier living environment.</li>
  <li><strong>How to Clean:</strong> Use a vacuum with a hose attachment to reach under furniture, ensuring all dust is removed.</li>
</ul>

<h3>Reclaim Your Time and Book a Guaranteed Clean with The Valley Clean Team Today</h3>
<p>Spring cleaning doesn't have to be overwhelming. With The Valley Clean Team, you can ensure these hidden areas are expertly addressed. Our veteran-owned, community-focused cleaning service in Athens, AL, provides precision and accountability with every clean. <strong>Stop worrying about the hidden grime—reclaim your time today.</strong> Book your guaranteed service and experience the elevated standard of cleanliness we deliver. <a href="#" title="Book Online Now">Book Online Now</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  ) : (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white border-t border-gray-100 shadow-inner">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-center">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-16 h-16 text-[#FFA985] mx-auto mb-6" />
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4 mt-0">Article Coming Soon!</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 m-0">This article is locked and scheduled to automatically publish on <br/><strong class="text-gray-800 text-xl">March 16 2026</strong>.<br/>Check back then!</p>
          <div class="mt-12">
            <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-lg font-semibold text-white bg-[#FFA985] rounded-full hover:bg-[#ff9a70] transition shadow-md no-underline">
              Back to Blog
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  )}
</BaseLayout>
